title: 1 BED 1 BATH HW SS  Message for video!
posting_body: This modern one bedroom, one bathroom in Wicker Park features an updated kitchen with granite counter tops and stainless steel appliances including a dishwasher, hardwood floors throughout, exposed brick wall, high ceilings, central air and heat.
This location is pet friendly, and has an on-site laundry facility.
The building is located close to the Division Blue Line, Clybourn Metra, New City shopping center is a short bus ride away and there are many restaurants and bars within walking distance.
The building is close to I-90 and Pulaski Park is across the street!
